<lb n="0754a02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 808 [No. 809]</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0754a03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說犢子經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0754a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0754a05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">吳月<note n="0754001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">氏＝支【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">氏【大】，支【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754001"><lem wit="【大】">氏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">支</rdg></app>優婆塞支謙<note n="0754002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（初）＋譯【元】【明】</note><note n="0754002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">譯【大】，初譯【元】【明】</note><app n="0754002"><lem wit="【大】">譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">初譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0754a06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT17p0754a0601">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754a0604" rend="inline">一時佛在舍衛國祇<note n="0754003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洹＝桓【三】【聖】</note><note n="0754003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洹【大】，桓【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0754003"><lem wit="【大】">洹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】">桓</rdg></app>阿那邠遲阿
<lb n="0754a07" ed="T"/>藍精舍。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754a0704" rend="inline">爾時佛<note n="0754004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇風患＝患風【宮】</note><note n="0754004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遇風患【大】，患風【宮】</note><app n="0754004"><lem wit="【大】">遇風患</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">患風</rdg></app>，當須牛乳。時有婆羅
<lb n="0754a08" ed="T"/>門大富，去城不遠。時佛遣阿難言：「汝往到婆
<lb n="0754a09" ed="T"/>羅門家從乞牛乳。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754a0908" rend="inline">阿難受教而往，<note n="0754005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754005"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0754006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝到【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至【大】，到【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754006"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">到</rdg></app>婆
<lb n="0754a10" ed="T"/>羅門家。婆羅門問阿難<note n="0754007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754007"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>：「來何所求？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754a1015" rend="inline">阿難
<lb n="0754a11" ed="T"/>言：「如來向者<note n="0754a1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">小【CB】【麗-CB】，少【大】</note><app n="0754a1101"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">小<note type="cf1">K11n0229_p0445a09</note><note type="cf2">Q11_p0125c13</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">少</rdg></app>遇風患，<note n="0754008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故遣我＝使我來【三】，故使我來【宮】</note><note n="0754008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故遣我【大】，使我來【宋】【元】【明】，故使我來【宮】</note><app n="0754008"><lem wit="【大】">故遣我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">使我來</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">故使我來</rdg></app>乞牛乳耳。」</p>
<lb n="0754a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0754a1201">婆羅門言：「牛在彼間，自𤚲取之。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754a1213" rend="inline">阿難即往到
<lb n="0754a13" ed="T"/>牛<note n="0754009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔群〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">群【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754009"><lem wit="【大】">群</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>所。<note n="0754010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有一〕－【三】，有一牸牛性常＝牛當【宮】</note><note n="0754010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有一牸牛性常【大】，牛當【宮】，牸牛性常【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0754010"><lem wit="【大】">有一牸牛，性常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">牛當</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">牸牛性常</rdg></app>弊惡，無人能近。阿
<lb n="0754a14" ed="T"/>難即自思惟：「我法不應自𤚲取牛乳。」</p>
<lb n="0754a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0754a1501">爾時帝釋知阿難所念，即來，化作婆羅門像，
<lb n="0754a16" ed="T"/>在牛邊立。阿難往倩言：「婆羅門！為我𤚲取牛
<lb n="0754a17" ed="T"/><note n="0754011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乳＋（婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳）【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0754011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->乳【大】＊，乳婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0754011"><lem wit="【大】">乳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">乳婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳</rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754a1702" rend="inline">語牛言：「如來遇小風患。汝與乳<note n="0754012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">湩＝𡦢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">湩【大】，𡦢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754012"><lem wit="【大】">湩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">𡦢</rdg></app>，令如
<lb n="0754a18" ed="T"/>來服之。差者，汝得福無量，不可稱計。如來者，
<lb n="0754a19" ed="T"/>是天上、天下之大師也。<note n="0754013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝常【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，常【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754013"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">常</rdg></app>以慈心憂念一切
<lb n="0754a20" ed="T"/>蠕動之類，欲令度脫一切苦惱。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754a2013" rend="inline">牛言：「此手捫
<lb n="0754a21" ed="T"/>摸我乳，一何快耶！前兩乳取去，置後兩乳用
<lb n="0754a22" ed="T"/>遺我子。我子朝來未有所食。」</p>
<lb n="0754a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0754a2301">爾時犢子在邊立住，聞有佛名，即語母言：「持
<lb n="0754a24" ed="T"/>我乳分盡用與佛。佛<note n="0754014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＋（是）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，者是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754014"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">者是</rdg></app>，天上、天下之大師也。
<lb n="0754a25" ed="T"/>甚難得值。我自食草，飲水，足得活耳。何以故？
<lb n="0754a26" ed="T"/>我先身以來常飲乳食，今<note n="0754015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝作畜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，作畜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754015"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">作畜</rdg></app>生牛身亦復飲
<lb n="0754a27" ed="T"/>乳。世間愚癡者甚多無量。我先世時坐隨惡
<lb n="0754a28" ed="T"/>知識教，不信佛經，使我作牛、作馬經十六劫，
<lb n="0754a29" ed="T"/>而今乃得聞有佛名。持我所<note n="0754016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（乳）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，食乳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754016"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食乳</rdg></app>分，盡用與佛，
<pb n="0754b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0808.0754b"/>
<lb n="0754b01" ed="T"/>滿器而去，令我後世智慧聰明，得道如佛。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754b0117" rend="inline">阿
<lb n="0754b02" ed="T"/>難持乳還至佛所。</p>
<lb n="0754b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0754b0301">佛問阿難：「彼牛母子有何言說？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754b0313" rend="inline">阿難言：「大可
<lb n="0754b04" ed="T"/>怪也。牛先甚<note n="0754017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754017"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>弊惡，不可得近。有一婆羅門
<lb n="0754b05" ed="T"/>為我𤚲乳，牛即調善。<note n="0754018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">母子＝子母【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">母子【大】，子母【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754018"><lem wit="【大】">母子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">子母</rdg></app>共說。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754b0513" rend="inline">佛言：「此牛
<lb n="0754b06" ed="T"/>子母先<note n="0754019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，世之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754019"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">世之</rdg></app>時不信佛經故，墮牛、馬中經十六
<lb n="0754b07" ed="T"/>劫。今乃得悟，聞有佛<note n="0754020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔名〕－【宋】【元】，明註曰南藏無名字</note><note n="0754020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】，明註曰南藏無名字</note><app n="0754020"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="【明】" wit="【南藏】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，<note n="0754021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使【宮】</note><note n="0754021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，使【宮】</note><app n="0754021"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">使</rdg></app><note n="0754022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【宮】</note><note n="0754022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0754022"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0754023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（我）＋慈【三】</note><note n="0754023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慈【大】，我慈【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0754023"><lem wit="【大】">慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">我慈</rdg></app>心，以乳
<lb n="0754b08" ed="T"/>施佛。彼牛母子後<note n="0754024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754024"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">身</rdg></app>，當為彌勒佛<note n="0754025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（作）＋沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙門【大】，作沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754025"><lem wit="【大】">沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">作沙門</rdg></app>弟
<lb n="0754b09" ed="T"/>子，得大羅漢。犢子死後，當為我懸繒、幡、蓋，散
<lb n="0754b10" ed="T"/>華，燒香，受持經戒。過二十劫後當作佛，名乳
<lb n="0754b11" ed="T"/>光如來，度脫一切。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0754b1108" rend="inline">佛言：「牛以好<note n="0754026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善心＝心善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善心【大】，心善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754026"><lem wit="【大】">善心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心善</rdg></app>意與佛
<lb n="0754b12" ed="T"/>乳故，度諸苦難，<note n="0754027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔後〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754027"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>得無量福報。以是因緣，
<lb n="0754b13" ed="T"/>佛不可不<note n="0754028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">信＝事【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">信【大】，事【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754028"><lem wit="【大】">信</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">事</rdg></app>，經不可不讀，道不可不學。普
<lb n="0754b14" ed="T"/>告天上、天下，皆悉令知。」</p></cb:div>
